__DESCRIPTION__

Showing some of the tools in the View menu of Padre, the Perl IDE.
Showing
- Line numbers
- Current line
- Project browser
- list of Functions
- Outline (pragmata, modules, methods)
- Automatic syntax checking
- Calltips

For more Padre related screencasts and to download Padre itself, please visit
[http://padre.perlide.org/](Padre, the Perl IDE)

[Perl tutorials](http://perlmaven.com/perl-tutorial)

